race.comment: TURN THE TIDE (6) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 8 lengths into second (37.47) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 over 650m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Good form should continue. PAW MANNY (1) is having first try over this longer journey. Scored last start (29.76) over 515m at Sandown. Looks suited here and can measure up. MITZI ROCKS (2) comes here off a placing in slick time (34.50) over 600m at this track. Bold showing expected again. ASCEND ECSTATIC (5) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.
